title: József Balázs
text:
József Balázs (born 9 May 1984 in <a href="Orosh%C3%A1za">Orosháza</a>) is a <a href="Hungarian%20people">Hungarian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="B%C3%A9k%C3%A9scsaba%201912%20El%C5%91re%20SE">Békéscsaba 1912 Előre SE</a>.
